Class AbstractOption

java.lang.Object
  pluginlib.AbstractOption
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractOption.BooleanOption, AbstractOption.ChoiceOption, AbstractOption.StringOption
public class AbstractOption
extends java.lang.Object

This is a base class for persistent options. The options are stored as workspace properties.

Author:
David R. Cok
